OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773162680
OL,3,CRape victim who accused wrong man says
OL,4,Cpolice dismissed doubts as 'trial
OL,5,Cnerves'
OL,7,FA rape victim told a court she had
OL,8,Fdoubts after picking out a man at an
OL,9,Fidentity parade who was later wrongly
OL,10,Fjailed for 17 years but was told by
OL,11,Fpolice it was just "trial nerves".
OL,13,FAndrew Malkinson was identified by the
OL,14,Fwoman after she was brutally attacked
OL,15,Fand raped in Little Hulton, Salford,
OL,16,Fin 2003.
OL,26,@sD@TOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
