PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773162680
OL,3,CRape victim who accused wrong man says
OL,4,Cpolice dismissed doubts as 'trial
OL,5,Cnerves'
OL,7,FHe then made two more attempts, in
OL,8,F2009 and 2018, to ask the Criminal
OL,9,FCases Review Commission to send his
OL,10,Fcase to the Court of Appeal, but both
OL,11,Ftimes were rejected.
OL,13,FHis final attempt in 2021 led to his
OL,14,Fappeal against his conviction being
OL,15,Fallowed by the Court of Appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
