PN,39810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773162680
OL,3,CRape victim who accused wrong man says
OL,4,Cpolice dismissed doubts as 'trial
OL,5,Cnerves'
OL,7,FJurors heard after news broke in July
OL,8,F2022, that detectives had linked an
OL,9,Funknown suspect through a DNA
OL,10,Fbreakthrough, police analysis of the
OL,11,Fdefendant's internet usage showed
OL,12,FQuinn had searched Google for, "Why do
OL,13,FI keep sweating all the time?" and
OL,14,F"How long is DNA kept in database?".
OL,16,FThe defendant has pleaded not guilty
OL,17,Fto two counts of rape, grievous bodily
OL,18,Fharm and attempting to choke or
OL,19,Fstrangle his victim to render her
OL,20,Funconscious while he carried out the
OL,21,Fattack.
OL,26,@tD@`OUuD@^O]vD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
